name: PatientUnableToCommunicateSNOMED
title: Patient Unable to Communicate (SNOMED)
description: This value set contains SNOMED concepts for patient inability to communicate
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains SNOMED concepts for patient inability to communicate),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify people who unable to communicate. This element may map to "Symptom" Category of the Quality Data Model.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts for inability to communicate using any means.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts for specific communication challenges (e.g., unable to communicate verbally).)
